    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-09-12T05:43:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-09-11T04:07:00-05:00" n="222"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d222">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/5194: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_RPS1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reinsch</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1919-09-12T06:43:00-04:00"
                            notBefore="1919-09-11T14:00:00+04:53">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received September 12, 1919, 6:43 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>From [<persName corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName> at] Omsk.</p>
                <p>“381. September 11, 2 p.m. General Siberian advance apparently <pb facs="0329"
                        n="217" xml:id="pg_217"/> now beginning. Northern army has advanced thirty
                    kilometres. Central army has inflicted heavy losses on Bolsheviki. Southern army
                    is within sixty versts of Kurgan. Last few days fighting resulted in Siberian
                    Army capturing 2,200 prisoners, 80 machine guns and 19 heavy guns. Bolsheviki
                    southern army are in flight. <persName corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName>.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RPS1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Reinsch</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
